Package: salmon
Title: Systems Analysis and Learning for inferring Modifiers of Networks 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Heeju", "Noh", email = "heeju.noh@chem.ethz.ch", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Rudiyanto", "Gunawan", email = "rudi.gunawan@chem.ethz.ch", role = "aut"))
Description: Systems Analysis and Learning for inferring Modifiers of Networks (SALMON) is a network based method for identifying molecular targets of drug treatments. SALMON provides the perturbation scores of proteins under a drug treatment of interest, using (time-series) gene expression data and prior network information (protein-gene network). 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
